China's @CansinoBio said on Wednesday that no serious blood clot cases had been reported so far in people who were injected with its #COVID19 vaccine. CanSinoBIO's shares fell as much as 13.7% and 18.4% in #Shanghai and #HongKong, respectively, in morning trading.
